       "<ul>\n          <li>We've started an experiment testing allowing people to pay for the <a href=\"https://buffer.com/awesome\">Awesome Plan</a> in Euros</li>\n          <li>We have continued our plan to <a href=\"https://open.bufferapp.com/retiring-suggestions/\">sunset the Suggestions feature</a></li>\n          <li>We've made some key speed and reliability improvements to <a href=\"https://buffer.com/business\">Buffer for Business</a></li>\n          <li>We have started to engage in sales conversations and set up customer success for larger business & enterprise</li>\n          <li>We're in the early stages of experimenting with a progress indicator in the onboarding flow</li>\n          <li>We're exploring ways to allow sharing multiple photos to Twitter and Facebook</li>\n        </ul>",
