       "Our vision at Buffer is to build the simplest and most powerful social media tool, and to set the bar\n        for great customer support. In addition to these product and service goals, we have a focus on building one\n        of the most unique and fulfilling workplaces that exist, by rethinking a lot of traditional practices.",
