       "\n          <p>We are still growing the team fast and have 14 open roles we are hiring for, including a\n          new role: We have started looking for an in-house finance person.</p>\n          <p>We received around 1,500 applications in August. (July and August tend to be slower in\n          terms of applications, we are excited for September.)</p>\n          <p>We will pass 50 people by the next update!</p>\n          <ul>\n            <li>42 total team members</li>\n            <li>5 new team members during August</li>\n            <li>8 more people will start or have started during September</li>\n          </ul>",
