     :body
       "\n        <p>This feels like a big milestone and a special moment to reflect on.</p>\n        <p>For me, the most exciting part of this is that 50 people are able to join our journey of working as a fully distributed\n        team, where you choose to live and work from the place which makes you happiest and most productive.</p>\n        <p>We've had several examples of teammates moving or traveling to find their happy place, or being able to move easily to help\n        and be with their significant other for studies or a job move.</p>",
