       "\n        <ul>\n          <li>We soft-launched improvements to our Pinterest scheduling capabilities, including letting you\n          pick an image from the page.</li>\n          <li>We made improvements to <a href=\"https://buffer.com/pablo\">Pablo</a>, our super-fast image creation\n          tool. A key one is that you can select text from a page and right click > Create Image with Pablo in\n          order to create an image with the selected quote over the top.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p>We're very close to rolling out the ability to schedule new 'Retweet with Comment' Tweets using\n          Buffer.</p>",
