            :updated-at "2015-11-20T08:00:46.000Z",
            :user-id "123456"}],
        :body
          "\n        <p>We had a really exciting month in terms of traffic and sign-ups. After we bared our souls and shared how\n        <a href=\"https://blog.bufferapp.com/lost-traffic\">we had been losing social media traffic for quite some time</a>,\n        we got a lot of great feedback, insights and encouragement.</p>\n        <p>In October we focused a lot on improving the calls to action on the blog, which had a lot of success.\n        We also dove in more on the paid ads side and hired someone full-time to help us with that-stay tuned for\n        updates!</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li>2,711 signups via blog content (17.2% growth)</li>\n          <li>1,252,000 unique visitors (18.4% growth)</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p><b>Break-out content hits:</b></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"https://blog.bufferapp.com/lost-traffic\">We've Lost Nearly Half Our Social Referral Traffic in the Last 12 Months</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://blog.bufferapp.com/twitter-polls\">The Complete Guide to New Twitter Polls: What They Are, How They Work and 9 Ways to Use Them</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://open.buffer.com/no-office/\">After Growing to 50 People, We're Ditching the Office Completely: Here's Why</a></li>\n        </ul>",
        :body-placeholder
          "List any notable marketing activities since the last update. How are your current marketing efforts performing? Anything new planned?",
        :created-at "2015-11-20T08:00:46.000Z",
